data.description: Looking for a brick home in Lakeland, than this one is a must see.  Home was renovated prior to current owners purchase in 2021.  Owner was told the following: new metal roof installed in 2019, HVAC and water heater installed in 2021.  Open floor plan with large great room for the entire family to enjoy.  Extra room is currently being used as a 4th bedroom but could also be an extra family room, gym, kids play room or even a home office.  You will love the secluded privacy fenced back yard with outbuilding.  Outbuilding has 3 separate areas to allow different usage, also has a carport attached.  You will also enjoy sitting on the large covered back patio and don't forget the firepit.  Currently 2 of the bedrooms are being used as storage/packing up.  Seller needs to remain in the home until December 1st.   Call today to see this home.
